frontmatter.title: The second biggest park in Barcelona

node.excerpt: A long while ago I bought a book called 111 Please In Barcelona That You Mush Not Miss and decided to take the challenge to see all these places. Especially during these times when we are not allowed to travel outside of Barcelona, it seems the perfect thing to do. Last night I picked no.78 Parc Central de Nou Barris.
